"Agent Fleet Management"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Centralized monitoring and governance of multiple AI agents across an organization. Fleet management includes agent registration, health monitoring, policy assignment, and activity dashboards."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Fleet Dashboard"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Agent Registry"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Multi-Agent Governance"}]]}],["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/use-cases","className":"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-violet-400 hover:underline mt-3","children":"Learn more →"}]]}],["$","div","6",{"id":"human-in-the-loop-hitl-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Human-in-the-Loop (HITL)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"A governance pattern where certain agent actions require explicit human approval before execution. In Vienna OS, T2 and T3 risk-tiered actions require one or more human approvers in the approval chain."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Approval Chain"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Multi-Party Approval"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Human Oversight"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","7",{"id":"t0-tier-zero-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"T0 (Tier Zero)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The lowest risk tier. Actions classified as T0 are auto-approved without human intervention. Examples: read-only queries, analytics lookups, status checks. T0 actions still generate audit trail entries."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Risk Tiering"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Auto-Approval"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","8",{"id":"t1-tier-one-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"T1 (Tier One)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Low-risk actions that require policy evaluation but not human approval. If the action matches an approved policy, it proceeds automatically. Examples: deploying to staging, sending notifications to internal teams."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Risk Tiering"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Policy-Approved"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","9",{"id":"t2-tier-two-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"T2 (Tier Two)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Medium-risk actions requiring at least one human approver. Examples: deploying to production, processing payments, modifying customer records. T2 warrants include approval timestamps and approver identity."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Risk Tiering"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Human Approval"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","10",{"id":"t3-tier-three-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"T3 (Tier Three)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Critical-risk actions requiring multi-party human approval, a written justification, and a rollback plan. Examples: wire transfers over $50K, bulk data deletion, infrastructure changes affecting multiple services. T3 is the highest governance tier."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Risk Tiering"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Multi-Party Approval"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Rollback Plan"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","11",{"id":"rollback-plan","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Rollback Plan"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"A required component of T3 warrant requests that specifies how to reverse the action if something goes wrong. The rollback plan is cryptographically linked to the warrant and can be triggered automatically or manually."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"T3"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Disaster Recovery"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Undo"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","12",{"id":"policy-as-code","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Policy-as-Code"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The practice of defining governance rules in machine-readable formats (JSON, YAML, or code) rather than human-written documents. Policy-as-code enables automated evaluation, version control, and audit trails for governance decisions."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Policy Engine"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Governance Automation"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","13",{"id":"warrant-scope","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Warrant Scope"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The boundaries defining what a warrant authorizes. Scope includes the action type, target resource, allowed parameters, maximum values, and geographic constraints. Any action outside the warrant scope is denied."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Execution Warrant"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Scope Verification"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","14",{"id":"warrant-ttl-time-to-live-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Warrant TTL (Time to Live)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The maximum duration a warrant remains valid after issuance. After the TTL expires, the warrant is automatically invalidated and the agent must request a new one. Default TTLs range from 60 seconds (T3) to 3600 seconds (T0)."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Execution Warrant"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Time-Limited Authorization"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","15",{"id":"truth-snapshot","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"Truth Snapshot"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"A cryptographic hash of the system state at the moment a warrant is issued. During post-execution verification, the truth snapshot is compared to the current state to detect unauthorized modifications."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Verification"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Tamper Detection"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"State Hash"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","16",{"id":"bsl-1-1-business-source-license-","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"BSL 1.1 (Business Source License)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"A source-available license that allows free use for evaluation, development, and non-production purposes. Production use requires a commercial license. After a specified date (2030 for Vienna OS), the license automatically converts to Apache 2.0."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Open Source"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Licensing"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Apache 2.0"}]]}],null]}],["$","div","17",{"id":"eu-ai-act","className":"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800/50 rounded-xl p-6 scroll-mt-24","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3","children":"EU AI Act"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"European Union regulation establishing a legal framework for artificial intelligence. The EU AI Act classifies AI systems by risk level and imposes requirements for transparency, human oversight, and accountability. Vienna OS helps organizations comply with high-risk AI system requirements."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-wrap gap-2","children":[["$","span","0",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Compliance"}],["$","span","1",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"Regulation"}],["$","span","2",{"className":"text-xs bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700/50 rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-slate-400","children":"AI Governance"}]]}],["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/blog/eu-ai-act-agent-compliance","className":"inline-flex items-center text-sm text-violet-400 hover:underline mt-3","children":"Learn more →"}]]}]]}]}]]}],null,["$","$L6",null,{"children":"$L7"}]]}],{},null,false]},null,false]},null,false],["$","$1","h",{"children":[null,["$","$1","o5zdQuIjFH3mu-EIA9vTO",{"children":[["$","$L8",null,{"children":"$L9"}],["$","$La",null,{"children":"$Lb"}],["$","meta",null,{"name":"next-size-adjust","content":""}]]}]]}],false]],"m":"$undefined","G":["$c","$undefined"],"s":false,"S":true}
